{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e89e6e4fbb","title":"中共中央、中央军委、中央文革小组转发“江西省革命委员会筹备小组注意工作方法”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"83f058f0d0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":17,"articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"}],"tags":[{"id":"1d084c925f","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题"},{"id":"aa690e5f54","name":"中共中央、中央军委、中央文革联合文件","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4353e7e73b","type":"title","text":"中共中央、中央军委、中央文革小组转发“江西省革命委员会筹备小组注意工作方法”","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"},{"id":"abdc0dc82b","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区革命委员会（筹备小组）、军管会、各大军区、省军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"},{"id":"1731e750b1","type":"paragraph","text":"江西省革命委员会筹备小组四条工作经验很好，现转发给你们作参考。其中第三条说到必须解决毛主席的声音传不下去的问题，此种现象在全国很多地方存在，望各地认真检查解决。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"},{"id":"3e0d0738e8","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"},{"id":"8e02e1b5d5","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"},{"id":"f456dc55e0","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"},{"id":"7082d84928","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年十一月十七日","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb"}],"page":{"id":"1a30287863","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e89e6e4fbb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}